  "text": "As mentioned in the introduction, uniform algorithms, such as the decay strategy from [CITATION_1] , solve local and global broadcast with optimal efficiency in the standard radio network model. A major focus of this paper is to prove that they work well in the dual graph model as well, if we assume a fading adversary with a reasonable stability factor.",
